'''Icyarabu''' (izina mu cyarabu : '''العربية ''' ) ni [[ururimi]] rw’[[abarabu]] na rwa [[Aligeriya]], [[Arabiya Sawudite]], [[Bahirayini]], [[Cade]], [[Eritereya]], [[Irake]], [[Isirayeli]], [[Jibuti]], [[Katari]], [[Komore]], [[Koweti]], [[Libani]], [[Libiya]], [[Maroke]], [[Misiri]], [[Moritaniya]], [[Nyarabu Zunze Ubumwe]], [[Omani]], [[Palestine]], [[Siriya]], [[Somaliya]], [[Sudani]], [[Tunisiya]], [[Yemeni]] na [[Yorudani]]. 

[[Abaisilamu]] bazi ko icyarabu ari rwo rurimi rwera.

